---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import Cta from '../components/Cta.astro';
---
<Base title="Domains of Development — The Qi-House">
  <PageHeader
    eyebrow="Our Educational Model"
    title="The domains of development."
    subtitle="A practical framework for building confidence, focus, communication, and self-governance."
  />

  <section class="bg-stone">
    <div class="container-content py-section-sm lg:py-section">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-14 reveal">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate/90">
          Real growth is more than a single skill. Our curriculum develops the whole person across several
          connected domains — awareness, discipline, communication, accountability, and leadership among
          them. These are not ranks or levels to clear. Every student carries the capacity for each, and
          progress is measured by how readily you can draw on the right capability for the moment in front
          of you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {Array.from({ length: 12 }).map((_, i) => (
          <div class="reveal border border-navy/10 bg-white rounded-sm p-6 hover:border-gold transition-colors">
            <div class="eyebrow !text-slate-400 mb-2">Domain {String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</div>
            <div class="font-display text-2xl text-navy mb-3">[Domain Name]</div>
            <p class="ph !p-3 !text-xs">[DOMAIN {i + 1}: plain one-line naming the capability this develops and the outcome a student gains — e.g. "Steadiness under pressure" → keeps composure when challenged]</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-slate/80 italic font-display text-xl mt-14 reveal">
        Progress shows up in everyday life: the ability to stay present, adapt to what a situation asks,
        and take responsibility for the outcome.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Cta title="See how the model develops you." text="The clearest way to understand our approach is to experience it. Schedule an assessment to discuss your goals and the pathway that fits them." />
</Base>
